# Rollups

- **`rollupProjectFinancials`**: Aggregates segment subtotals into `CostingProject.totalHPP` / `totalSelling` using margin/overhead settings. Do not duplicate this logic in API routes.
- **`manual-costing-rollup.ts`**: Manual segments — keep consistent with AHU rollup expectations for quotations.

Related: `lib/cost-summary.ts` (pure helpers) — keep formulas aligned with UI expectations.
